import React from 'react'
import './App.css'
import {BrowserRouter as Router, Link, Route, Redirect, Switch, BrowserRouter} from 'react-router-dom'
import Login from'./Component/Login'
import SignUp from './Component/SignUp'
import Start from './project/Start'
import Protect from './Component/Protect'
import Begin from './Component/Begin'
import Footer from './Component/Footer'
import NotFound from './Component/NotFound'
import Logout from './Component/Logout'

export default class App extends React.PureComponent {
  render() {
    return (
      <BrowserRouter>
      <Switch>
       
        
        {
            localStorage.getItem("login") ? <Route path="/login"> <Redirect to="/"/></Route>: null 
        }
        {
            localStorage.getItem("login") ? <Route path="/signup"> <Redirect to="/"/></Route>: null
        }
          <Protect exact path="/" component={Begin}/>

          <Route path="/login"
              render={props => (
                  <Login {...props} />
              )}>
          </Route>
          <Route path="/signup" component={SignUp}/>
          
          <Route path="/logout" component={Logout}/>
          <Footer/>

          <Route path='/404' component={NotFound} />
     
      </Switch>
      </BrowserRouter>
    )
  }
}
